[{"Id": 1011860, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Slaughtering an animal (Qurbani) in other places (then Mina) is mustahab. If the animal of sacrifice is camel or cow, it must be a female. If it is a ram (lamb) or a goat it must be male. The camel should have entered its 6th year. In cow and goat the precaution is that it should have entered the 3rd year. Sheep must have entered the 2nd year. The sacrificial animal must not have any damaged part. That it must not have a broken horn or cut ear. Sacrifice of castrated animal and ones raised as domestic animals, is detestable (makrooh). At the time of offering the sacrifice, turn the animal face towards Qibla, recite dua <Wajjahto wajheya lillazee> and then slaughter.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jaanwar ki qurbani dusri jagoh par (Mina ke alawa) mustahab hai. Agar qurbani Oonth ya Gai (Camel or Cow) ki hai to woh Nar (female) hona chahiye, aur agar Memne ya Bakre (Lamb or Goat) ki hai to woh Maada (male) hona chahiye. Qurbani ka Oonth (camel) ki umr (age) 5 saal pura ho kar 6th saal laga ho, Gai ya Bakre (Cow or Goat) ki umr 2 saal pura ho kar 3rd saal laga ho aur Behed (Sheep) ki umr saal pura ho kar 2nd saal laga ho. Qurbani ka jaanwar aiyb-daar nahi hona chahiye, yaani uski singh (horn) tooti huwi na ho aur uska kaan (ear) kata huwa na ho. Khassi ya paaltu (paley huwe) jaanwar ki qurbani makrooh hai. Qurbani karte waqt jaanwar ka rukh Qible ki taraf kare, aur dua <Wajjahto wajheya lillazee> ko padhe aur phir zibah kare.", "UrduDescription": "جانور کی قربانی دوسری جگہوں پر (منٰی کے علاوہ) مستحب ہے۔ اگر قربانی اونٹ یا گائے کی ہے تو وہ نر ہونا چاہیے، اور اگر میمنے یا بکرے کی ہے تو وہ مادی ہونا چاہیے۔ قربانی کا اونٹ کی عمر ۵ سال پورا ہو کر چھٹا سال لگا ہو، گائے یا بکرے کی عمر ۲ سال پورا ہو کر تیسرا سال لگا ہو اور بھیڑ کی عمر سال پورا ہو کر دوسرا سال لگا ہو۔ قربانی کا جانور عیب دار نہی ہونا چاہیے، یعنی اسکی سینگ ٹوٹی ہوئی نہ ہو اور اس کا کان کٹا ہوا نہ ہو۔ خصی یا پالتو جانور کی قربانی مکروہ ہے۔ قربانی کرتے وقت جانور کا رخ قبلہ کی طرف کرے اور دُعا <وَجَّہْتُ وَجْہِیَ لِلَّذِیْ> کو پڑھے اور پھر ذبح کرے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign